
** Noarchive Log

  - A database in norarchive log mode cannot be backuped if the
    database is open. So connecting to the database with ONS is not
    possible. Target must be '/'.

  <example>
    $ rman TARGET=/ CATALOG=rman/rman@first
    RMAN> shutdown;
    RMAN> startup mount;
    RMAN> backup database;
    RMAN> alter database open;
  </example>

Back to OracleRman.
